304
00:18:19,700 --> 00:18:22,620
Then your face must be

305
00:18:23,420 --> 00:18:24,340
hard as armor.

306
00:18:25,380 --> 00:18:26,580
Put it down.

307
00:18:26,900 --> 00:18:28,140
You can do neither of them.

308
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:29,100
