321
00:19:05,820 --> 00:19:07,300
Don't scare him away.

322
00:19:08,060 --> 00:19:08,900
Understand?

323
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:13,380
Wait.

324
00:19:14,900 --> 00:19:16,060
Well...

325
00:19:16,580 --> 00:19:18,260
