328
00:19:22,380 --> 00:19:23,500
I'll pay for it.

329
00:19:29,140 --> 00:19:29,980
Look at you.

330
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:31,780
You don't have to do this.

331
00:19:34,700 --> 00:19:36,660
Welcome to Greater World!

332
00:19:38,660 --> 00:19:40,020
