348
00:20:27,060 --> 00:20:27,900
My Lord.

349
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:33,820
Carefree Powder?

350
00:20:35,300 --> 00:20:36,740
Is she also an addict?

351
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:38,580
Guazi's mother.

352
