369
00:21:41,820 --> 00:21:43,900
But how could you abandon your wife?

370
00:21:45,300 --> 00:21:46,140
Madam Wang,

371
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:47,300
he's not...

372
00:21:48,900 --> 00:21:49,820
Idiot,

373
00:21:50,260 --> 00:21:51,100
