right?

403
00:23:20,180 --> 00:23:21,100
My Lord.

404
00:23:21,860 --> 00:23:23,300
Lan Che told me

405
00:23:23,700 --> 00:23:25,900
you pretended to be the leader
of the bandits in Liangzhou

406
00:23:26,140 --> 00:23:27,540
