425
00:24:07,220 --> 00:24:08,860
That's right. What am I doing?

426
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:11,460
Sir, I'm here to get my medicine.

427
00:24:15,140 --> 00:24:15,980
My Lady,

428
00:24:16,500 --> 00:24:18,460
