430
00:24:21,140 --> 00:24:22,620
It's my mother's hairpin.

431
00:24:22,780 --> 00:24:24,740
I think it's from Liangzhou.

432
00:24:25,140 --> 00:24:26,380
It's hard

433
00:24:26,380 --> 00:24:28,060
