434
00:24:30,980 --> 00:24:32,580
Why does it look familiar to you?

435
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:35,100
I...

436
00:24:37,740 --> 00:24:38,740
Many people come and go

437
00:24:38,740 --> 00:24:39,940
