516
00:28:14,300 --> 00:28:16,420
I'm dying anyway.

517
00:28:17,700 --> 00:28:19,340
I finally killed him.

518
00:28:19,740 --> 00:28:21,780
It's all worth it!

519
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:44,260
You...

520
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:47,940
